{"tid":1161740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Bob叔=連登契爺 達哥=連登契哥","createTime":"2019-05-19T11:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T07:17:25.000Z","uid":55552,"like":60,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"891be9f5ccf279a87f5bd4a2a00e47dea8e135d4","tid":1161740,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">普通人炒樓</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔：攞必需品嚟炒，正一吸血鬼，炒樓狗死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Bob叔開埋間公司嚟炒樓</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔：正途搵錢，炒樓不知高尚過接廣告幾多，有咩理由反<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NXjb9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NXjb9L.png&h=e1839c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XOgsk12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOgsk12.png&h=4a23e390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">普通人係連登打錯一隻殘體字</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔：支那狗死全家/死支那狗躝返百度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">達哥直播對住六千個細蚊仔用殘體字幕</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔：咁支持本土文化又唔見你乜乜乜乜&hellip;&hellip;/你哋細個打機咪又用殘體字幕！，睇過一粒殘體字幕嘅人都無資格反達哥！你哋根本係恰鳩我達<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFRG9X5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFRG9X5.png&h=4c5c22fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而家諗返起杜生真係啲唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n杜生呀杜生，如果你好似上面兩位咁受連登仔歡迎，連登仔幫你含吹奶啜都制啦。<br />\n<br />\n咩炒樓呀，係幾千個細蚊仔面前合理化殘體字呀，拖下糧呀呢啲又算得啲乜呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ad93c784c922e5bbe03e15634dabb1c44215c977","tid":1161740,"uid":142676,"like":6,"dislike":22,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"人地有個人魅力<br />\n普通人有無呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9146011f51b31a516e58f504ace492f80744fa68","tid":1161740,"uid":28042,"like":12,"dislike":19,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"冇反過人炒樓，有得俾人炒係政府錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾你渣住大舊錢你唔炒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個濕鳩政府唔識修例垃撚圾姐"},{"pid":"9c19200f541bb39afb3aefa9e5248bac058984ee","tid":1161740,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:01:48.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛咁多紅線<br />\n一觸及左就要反<br />\n你做人唔辛苦？<br />\n人地受歡迎係佢地本事"},{"pid":"e77ed0652938fca7bd2c9d7d090aa6c842bb12d4","tid":1161740,"uid":58140,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"辛苦樓主了 打咁大段嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64209ce0834e6ffed4d3f51917900ad59161471","tid":1161740,"uid":65201,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:05:35.000Z","msg":"反得杜生既其實都係支持共產黨，無咩需要講"},{"pid":"df7815a09facc8bc6528f2fa387dbdf5ace060bf","tid":1161740,"uid":55552,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"ad93c784c922e5bbe03e15634dabb1c44215c977","tid":1161740,"uid":142676,"like":6,"dislike":22,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"人地有個人魅力<br />\n普通人有無呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"第一次見人將雙重標準，對人不對事講得咁理直氣壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c51d452d504fb5523cabc99931b5ab7831eae2","tid":1161740,"uid":55552,"like":